---
title: Pesto Baked Salmon with Herby Couscous and Garlicky Veggies
description: Juicy, oven-baked salmon gets topped with herby pesto and served over fluffy, herby pearl couscous. This is a meal for everyone that's perfect for a quick weeknight dinner or a picnic at the park!
